          h1.divide-section  Pagination
          p.article-lead Easlily create a nicely looking pagination to navigate through pages.
          h2 Usage
          p
            | The Pagination component consists of button-like styled links, that are aligned side by side.
          table.table
            thead
              tr
                th Class
                th Description
            tbody
              tr
                td
                  code .pagination
                td
                  | Add this class to a
                  code <ul>
                  | element to define the Pagination component. Use
                  code <a>
                  | elements as pagination items within the list.
              tr
                td
                  code .active
                td
                  | Add this class to a list item to apply an active state and use a
                  code <span>
                  | instead of an
                  code <a>
                  | element.
              tr
                td
                  code .disabled
                td
                  | Add this class to a list item to apply a disabled state and use a
                  code <span>
                  | instead of an
                  code <a>
                  | element.
          p
            | To apply an ellipsis without any styling, just use a
            code <span>
            | element instead of an
            code <a>
            | element.
          h3.tm-article-subtitle Example
          ul.pagination
            li.disabled
              span
                i.icon-angle-double-left
            li.active
              span 1
            li
              a(href='#') 2
            li
              a(href='#') 3
            li
              a(href='#') 4
            li
              span ...
            li
              a(href='#') 20
            li
              a(href='#')
                i.icon-angle-double-right
          h3.tm-article-subtitle Markup
          pre.
            
          hr.article-divider
          h2 Alignment modifiers
          p
            | Add the
            code .pagination-left
            | or
            code .pagination-right
            | class to the pagination to align it left or right.
