          h2 Previous and next
          p
            | Creating a simple previous and next pagination is very easy. Just add the
            code .pagination-previous
            | or
            code .pagination-next
            | class to a
            code <li>
            | element to align previous and next buttons left or right.
          h4.tm-article-subtitle Example
          ul.pagination
            li.pagination-previous
              a(href='#')
                i.icon-angle-double-left
                | Previous
            li.pagination-next
              a(href='#')
                | Next
                i.icon-angle-double-right
